CeboFik Primo u jednom sloju, sa kratkodlakim valjkom, razblaženim 20% vodom i sačekajte potpuno sušenje (6-8 sati).'),(4244,460,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(4245,460,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details','1'),(4246,460,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details','field_61753d07a8579'),(4247,460,'instructions_stages_1_instruction_label_title','CeboMarmo aplikacija, KLASIČNI KAMEN'),(4248,460,'_instructions_stages_1_instruction_label_title','field_61753cf8a8578'),(4249,460,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','462'),(4250,460,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(4251,460,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','463'),(4252,460,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(4253,460,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','PIETRA CLASSICA\r\nNanesite prvi sloj obojenog CeboMarma inox gleterom, ukrštenim gletericama kako biste dobili glatku i ujednačenu površinu. Sačekajte potpuno sušenje (6-8 h).'),(4254,460,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(4255,460,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_image_f','464'),(4256,460,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(4257,460,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_image_s',''),(4258,460,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(4259,460,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_text','Nakon otprilike 4 sata, nanesite treći sloj CeboMarma u boji inox gletericom, ukrštenim potezima po celoj površini.\r\nPređite inox gletericom, pritiskajući proizvod, da biste zabeleli proizvod.'),(4260,460,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(4261,460,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details','2'),(4262,460,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details','field_61753d07a8579'),(4263,460,'instructions_stages_2_instruction_label_title','Poliranje'),(4264,460,'_instructions_stages_2_instruction_label_title','field_61753cf8a8578'),(4265,460,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','465'),(4266,460,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(4267,460,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','466'),(4268,460,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(4269,460,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','<strong>OPCIJA 1</strong> - Ručno poliranje -:\r\nPre potpunog sušenja polirajte površinu savršeno čistom inox gletericom.\r\n\r\n<strong>OPCIJA 2</strong> - Mašinsko poliranje -:\r\nNakon najmanje 2-4 sata od nanošenja poslednjeg sloja CeboMarma, poliranje izvedite abrazivnim diskovima u nizu:\r\n1. zrno 2.000\r\n2. zrno 4.000\r\n\r\n<strong>NAPOMENA</strong>: Nakon mašinskog poliranja i dalje je potrebno ručno poliranje inox gleterom.'),(4270,460,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(4271,460,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details','1'),(4272,460,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details','field_61753d07a8579'),(4273,460,'instructions_stages_3_instruction_label_title','Zaštita i konačno poliranje'),(4274,460,'_instructions_stages_3_instruction_label_title','field_61753cf8a8578'),(4275,460,'instructions_stages_3_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','467'),(4276,460,'_instructions_stages_3_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(4277,460,'instructions_stages_3_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s',''),(4278,460,'_instructions_stages_3_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(4279,460,'instructions_stages_3_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','CeboVax: završna obrada za unutrašnjost na bazi pčelinjeg voska, prozračna i vodoodbojna.\r\nNanesite sloj CeboVax -a razblažen 1: 1 sa vodom, koristeći sintetički sundjer. Nanesite vosak prateći smer obrade: odmah zatim mekom krpom pređite preko površine da biste uklonili višak voska.\r\nSačekajte 10-15 minuta i ispolirajte površinu više puta prolazeći kroz savršeno čistu čeličnu gletericu, pritiskajući odgovarajući pritisak.'),(4280,460,'_instructions_stages_3_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(4281,460,'instructions_stages_3_instructions_details','1'),(4282,460,'_instructions_stages_3_instructions_details','field_61753d07a8579'),(4283,460,'instructions_stages','4'),(4284,460,'_instructions_stages','field_61753c82a8577'),(4285,460,'half_section_f',''),(4286,460,'_half_section_f','field_61771b4aae9d1'),(4287,460,'half_section_s',''),(4288,460,'_half_section_s','field_61771b6cae9d2'),(4289,460,'background_image','344'),(4290,460,'_background_image','field_617722e02e7b3'),(4291,460,'main_content','<h2>Katalozi</h2>\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost/zidnedekoracije-new/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Cebos_S.A._CeboMarmo_Pietra_Classica.pdf\">Cebos_S.A._CeboMarmo_Pietra_Classica</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost/zidnedekoracije-new/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/S.T.-CEBOMARMO.pdf\">S.T.-CEBOMARMO</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost/zidnedekoracije-new/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/IT_S_S_-04_049_CLP_1-CEBOMARMO.pdf\">IT_S_S_-04_049_CLP_1-CEBOMARMO</a>'),(4292,460,'_main_content','field_617724162e7b9'),(4293,460,'full_width_section',''),(4294,460,'_full_width_section','field_6177246f65aab'),(4295,460,'_yoast_wpseo_primary_kategorija-proizvoda','6'),(4296,460,'_yoast_wpseo_estimated-reading-time-minutes',''),(4297,471,'_wp_attached_file','2021/11/Pietra-Classica.jpg'),(4298,471,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"widt