r\n\r\nPogodni su gipsani i građevinski premazi ili oni sa prethodnim lakiranjem, prikladno obnovljeni od prašine i oštećenja.\r\n\r\n-U prisustvu nedavno gletovanih površina, novih zidova i posebno upijajućih podloga ili podloga sa krečom, nanesite preventivni sloj CeboFix M, prozirnog akrilnog učvršćivača, razređenog 1: 1 zapreminski vodom, četkom.'),(4766,524,'_instructions_section_description','field_61753c63a8576'),(4767,524,'instructions_stages_0_instruction_label_title','Datalji za nanošenje boje'),(4768,524,'_instructions_stages_0_instruction_label_title','field_61753cf8a8578'),(4769,524,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','529'),(4770,524,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(4771,524,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s',''),(4772,524,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(4773,524,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','Na gips, gips karton ili prethodno obojene podloge nanesite CeboFix Primo, pigmentirani akrilni prajmer, pogodan za ravne površine sa hromatskim razlikama i razlikama u upijanju. CeboFix Primo se može koristiti u beloj ili obojenoj boji, kako bi se olakšalo nanošenje i prekrivanje naknadne završne obrade, a može se nanositi valjkom ili četkom, u jednom sloju, razblaženo 20-30% zapremine vodom.'),(4774,524,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(4775,524,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_image_f','529'),(4776,524,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(4777,524,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_image_s',''),(4778,524,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(4779,524,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_text','CeboTop Lak Active se takođe može primeniti na metale, drvo i plastiku: u tim slučajevima potrebno je pripremiti podloge sa odgovarajućim prajmerima.\r\n\r\nUpotreba u okruženjima sa prisustvom hrane (HACCP)\r\n\r\nCeboTop Lak Active Satin je klasifikovan kao sistem za farbanje, pogodan za okruženja u kojima postoji hrana, prema normi UNI 11021. Sertifikat je dostupan na zahtev.'),(4780,524,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(4781,524,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details','2'),(4782,524,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details','field_61753d07a8579'),(4783,524,'instructions_stages','1'),(4784,524,'_instructions_stages','field_61753c82a8577'),(4785,524,'half_section_f','<h2>Karta boja</h2>\r\nPrikazane boje su napravljene pomoću digitalnih aplikacija, stoga ih treba smatrati indikativnim i neobavezujućim. Za tačan izbor boja, pogledajte ton karte boja sa pravim proizvodom, koji su dostupni kod ovlašćenih Cebos prodavaca boja.'),(4786,524,'_half_section_f','field_61771b4aae9d1'),(4787,524,'half_section_s','<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-522\" src=\"http://localhost/zidnedekoracije-new/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/karta-boja-cebotop-lak-active-opaco.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"345\" />'),(4788,524,'_half_section_s','field_61771b6cae9d2'),(4789,524,'background_image',''),(4790,524,'_background_image','field_617722e02e7b3'),(4791,524,'main_content',''),(4792,524,'_main_content','field_617724162e7b9'),(4793,524,'full_width_section',''),(4794,524,'_full_width_section','field_6177246f65aab'),(4795,524,'_yoast_wpseo_primary_kategorija-proizvoda','6'),(4796,524,'_yoast_wpseo_content_score','60'),(4797,524,'_yoast_wpseo_estimated-reading-time-minutes',''),(4798,529,'_wp_attached_file','2021/11/w8gaJq3.jpeg'),(4799,529,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:469;s:6:\"height\";i:267;s:4:\"file\";s:20:\"2021/11/w8gaJq3.jpeg\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:2:{s:6:\"medium\";