gućava beskonačan broj ličnih završnih obrada prema boji boje i kombinaciji različitih vrsta sjaja.'),(4970,541,'_page_main_content_description','field_6175355dc93bd'),(4971,541,'order_product_description',''),(4972,541,'_order_product_description','field_61753591c93be'),(4973,541,'instructions_section_title','Uputstvo za upotrebu'),(4974,541,'_instructions_section_title','field_61753bffa8575'),(4975,541,'instructions_section_description','CeboSpark se može nanositi na gips ili fine maltere, sve dok je prikladno pripremljeno. Razblažite proizvod 20% vodom i nanesite u dva sloja pomoću odgovarajuće CeboSi četke, dostupne u veličinama 2½ i 4 inča, ukrštenim potezima četke. Sačekajte potpuno sušenje (6-8 sati) između slojeva.'),(4976,541,'_instructions_section_description','field_61753c63a8576'),(4977,541,'instructions_stages_0_instruction_label_title','CeboMagic'),(4978,541,'_instructions_stages_0_instruction_label_title','field_61753cf8a8578'),(4979,541,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f',''),(4980,541,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(4981,541,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s',''),(4982,541,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(4983,541,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Dodatak u pasti za enterijere, zasnovan na holografskim mikro-sjajima sa zadivljujućim trodimenzionalnim efektom i šarenim izgledom. Dodavanjem u CeboSpark daje površinama dodir magije. Pomešajte CeboMagic sa CeboSpark -om neposredno pre nanošenja. Pripremljeni mešani proizvod mora se primeniti u roku od 6 dana.</span>'),(4984,541,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(4985,541,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details','1'),(4986,541,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details','field_61753d07a8579'),(4987,541,'instructions_stages_1_instruction_label_title','CeboGliss'),(4988,541,'_instructions_stages_1_instruction_label_title','field_61753cf8a8578'),(4989,541,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f',''),(4990,541,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(4991,541,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s',''),(4992,541,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(4993,541,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','Aditiv u prahu za enterijere, na bazi laminiranih sjaja. Kada se doda u CeboSpark, finišu daje blistav izgled. Dodavanje CeboGlissa\r\nmora da se uradi neposredno pre ugradnje. Pripremljeni mešani proizvod mora se primeniti u roku od 6 dana.\r\nPovršinska obrada\r\n\r\nUverite se da su podloge savršeno čiste, suve i ujednačene. U slučaju nedavno popravljenih zidova, visoko upijajućih ili kredastih podloga, pažljivo očistite površinu i nanesite sloj temeljnog premaza koji izolira fiksator CeboFix M, četkom, razblažen vodom 1: 1.'),(4994,541,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(4995,541,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details','1'),(4996,541,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details','field_61753d07a8579'),(4997,541,'instructions_stages_2_instruction_label_title','FondoPlus'),(4998,541,'_instructions_stages_2_instruction_label_title','field_61753cf8a8578'),(4999,541,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f',''),(5000,541,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(5001,541,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s',''),(5002,541,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(5003,541,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','Osnovni akrilni premaz na vodenoj bazi sa visokim svojstvima prekrivanja i sjajno bele boje. Pažljivo očistite podlogu i nanesite jedan ili dva sloja proizvoda, sa kratkodlakim valjkom, sve dok površina ne bude potpuno prekrivena. Nanesite CeboSpark kada se FondoPlus potpuno osuši.'),(5004,541,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(5005,541,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details','1'),(5006,541,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details','field_61753d07a8579'),(5007,541,'instructions_stages_3_instruction_label_title','CeboVitra Piu'),(5008,541,'_instructions_stages_3_instruction_label_title','field_61753cf8a8578'),(5009,541,'instructions_stages_3_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f',''),(5010,541,'_instructions_stages_3_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(5011,541,'instructions_stages_3_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s',''),(5012,541,'_instructions_stages_3_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(5013,541,'instructions_stages_3_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','Zaštitna poliuretanska zaštita na vodenoj bazi, providna, sjajna. Pogodno za unutrašnju i spoljašnju upotrebu; obrađene površine se izuzetno peru i otporne su na ogrebotine. Pogodno za zaštitu površina podložnih čestim operacijama čišćenja. Spreman za upotrebu, nanesite CeboVitra Piu u dva sloja kratkodlakim valjkom.'),(5014,541,'_instructions_stages_3_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(5015,541,'instructions_stages_3_instructions_details','1'),(5016,541,'_instructions_stages_3_instructions_details','field_61753d07a8579'),(5017,541,'instructions_stages','4'),(5018,541,'_instructions_stages','field_61753c82a8577'),(5019,541,'half_section_f','<h2>Karta boja</h2>\r\nPrikazane boje su napravljene pomoću digitalnih aplikacija, stoga ih treba smatrati indikativnim i neobavezujućim. Za tačan izbor