zravnali površinu.'),(5962,608,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(5963,608,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details','1'),(5964,608,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details','field_61753d07a8579'),(5965,608,'instructions_stages_3_instruction_label_title','Ciklus primene peskarenog efekta'),(5966,608,'_instructions_stages_3_instruction_label_title','field_61753cf8a8578'),(5967,608,'instructions_stages_3_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f',''),(5968,608,'_instructions_stages_3_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(5969,608,'instructions_stages_3_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s',''),(5970,608,'_instructions_stages_3_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(5971,608,'instructions_stages_3_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','<strong>Ciklus primene peskarenog efekta</strong>\r\nNanesite CeboStone, obojen u istoj boji kao i završni sloj, u jednom sloju, srednjom četkom (7 × 3 ili 10 × 3); rad sa ukrštenim potezima četke kako biste dobili naizmeničnu rustikalnu i glatkiju površinu na površini. Sačekajte potpuno sušenje. Nanesite CeboSi Universal sa posebnom CeboSi četkom, na isti način kako je opisano za glatki efekat.'),(5972,608,'_instructions_stages_3_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(5973,608,'instructions_stages_3_instructions_details','1'),(5974,608,'_instructions_stages_3_instructions_details','field_61753d07a8579'),(5975,608,'instructions_stages_4_instruction_label_title','Ciklus primene Spatolato efekta'),(5976,608,'_instructions_stages_4_instruction_label_title','field_61753cf8a8578'),(5977,608,'instructions_stages_4_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f',''),(5978,608,'_instructions_stages_4_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(5979,608,'instructions_stages_4_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s',''),(5980,608,'_instructions_stages_4_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(5981,608,'instructions_stages_4_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','<strong>Ciklus primene Spatolato efekta</strong>\r\nNanesite CeboStrong gletericom od nerđajućeg čelika: ravnomerno rasporedite proizvod po površini; zatim postići estetski efekat predstavljen radom lopaticom u ukrštenim i nepravilnim potezima. Kad proizvod prosuši, pređite preko površine kako biste lakše skinulu reljefne delove. Sačekajte potpuno sušenje. Nanesite CeboSi Universal sunđerom, u dva sloja, razblažen 10% vodom: umočite alat u proizvod i ravnomerno kružnim pokretima nanesite na površinu.'),(5982,608,'_instructions_stages_4_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(5983,608,'instructions_stages_4_instructions_details','1'),(5984,608,'_instructions_stages_4_instructions_details','field_61753d07a8579'),(5985,608,'instructions_stages_5_instruction_label_title','Ciklus primene Sbrecciato efekta'),(5986,608,'_instructions_stages_5_instruction_label_title','field_61753cf8a8578'),(5987,608,'instructions_stages_5_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f',''),(5988,608,'_instructions_stages_5_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(5989,608,'instructions_stages_5_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s',''),(5990,608,'_instructions_stages_5_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(5991,608,'instructions_stages_5_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','<strong>Ciklus primene Sbrecciato efekta</strong>\r\nNanesite CeboStrong gletericom od nerđajućeg čelika ujednačene debljine 1-2 mm. Dok je proizvod još mokar, obradite površinu posebnim CeboSign alatom kako biste imitirali usitnjeno kamenje. Da biste postigli prirodniji efekat, radite na nepravilan način, izbegavajući ponavljanje dizajna. Pre nego što se proizvod potpuno osuši, zagladite površinu gleterom, lagano stežući reljefno del