ost.\r\n\r\nAkrilna završna obrada na vodenoj bazi, periva, idealna za sve vrste zidnih podloga. CeboStone Metal vam omogućava da lako stvarate fine dekoracije, gde je efekat peskarenja pojačan dragocenošću metalnog izgleda, sa nizom delikatnih senki i fascinantnih zlatnih odsjaja.'),(6200,624,'_page_main_content_description','field_6175355dc93bd'),(6201,624,'order_product_description',''),(6202,624,'_order_product_description','field_61753591c93be'),(6203,624,'instructions_section_title','Uputstvo za upotrebu'),(6204,624,'_instructions_section_title','field_61753bffa8575'),(6205,624,'instructions_section_description','Priprema podloga:\r\n\r\nProverite da li su podloge ujednačene, savršeno čiste i suve. U prisustvu nedavno gletovanih, krečnih ili upijajućih podloga, izvršite savršeno čišćenje podloge i prethodno nanesite izolacioni fiksator CeboFix M u jednom sloju, četkom, razblažen 1:1 sa vodom.'),(6206,624,'_instructions_section_description','field_61753c63a8576'),(6207,624,'instructions_stages_0_instruction_label_title','CeboIron Grigio'),(6208,624,'_instructions_stages_0_instruction_label_title','field_61753cf8a8578'),(6209,624,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f',''),(6210,624,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(6211,624,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s',''),(6212,624,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(6213,624,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','<strong>CeboIron Grigio</strong>\r\nAkrilna završna obrada na vodenoj bazi za unutrašnjost, poluprozirna, sa pigmentima od liskuna i sedefa.'),(6214,624,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(6215,624,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details','1'),(6216,624,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details','field_61753d07a8579'),(6217,624,'instructions_stages_1_instruction_label_title','FondoPlus'),(6218,624,'_instructions_stages_1_instruction_label_title','field_61753cf8a8578'),(6219,624,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f',''),(6220,624,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(6221,624,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s',''),(6222,624,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(6223,624,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','<strong>FondoPlus</strong>\r\nAkrilni prajmer na vodenoj bazi, sa visokim prekrivanjem i belinom. Nanesite proizvod kratkodlakim valjkom, u jednom ili dva sloja, dok podloga ne bude potpuno prekrivena. Nakon što se FondoPlus osuši, nastavite sa nanošenjem CeboStone Metal.'),(6224,624,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(6225,624,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details','1'),(6226,624,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details','field_61753d07a8579'),(6227,624,'instructions_stages_2_instruction_label_title','Ciklus primene'),(6228,624,'_instructions_stages_2_instruction_label_title','field_61753cf8a8578'),(6229,624,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f',''),(6230,624,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(6231,624,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s',''),(6232,624,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(6233,624,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','<strong>Ciklus primene</strong>\r\nNanesite CeboStone Metal u naznačenom razblaženju, u jednom sloju, srednjom četkom (7 × 3 ili 10 × 3), radeći ukrštenim potezima četke kako biste dobili naizmenično peščane i glatke površine na površini.\r\nDekoraciju je moguće d