u vodene pare: Sd m 0,026</li>\r\n 	<li>Difuzija vodene pare V g / m2 d 786; referentna vrednost: V&gt; = 150 visoka propustljivost.</li>\r\n</ul>'),(7034,687,'_page_main_content_description','field_6175355dc93bd'),(7035,687,'order_product_description',''),(7036,687,'_order_product_description','field_61753591c93be'),(7037,687,'instructions_section_title','Uputstvo za upotrebu'),(7038,687,'_instructions_section_title','field_61753bffa8575'),(7039,687,'instructions_section_description','Priprema podloga:\r\n\r\nPogodni su svi gipsani, krečni i građevinski premazi. Proverite da li su sredstva savršeno čista, suva i ujednačena po izgledu i upijanju.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-690\" src=\"http://localhost/zidnedekoracije-new/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/emissioni-negli-ambienti-interni-e1531398338197.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"80\" />'),(7040,687,'_instructions_section_description','field_61753c63a8576'),(7041,687,'instructions_stages_0_instruction_label_title','CeboFix R'),(7042,687,'_instructions_stages_0_instruction_label_title','field_61753cf8a8578'),(7043,687,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f',''),(7044,687,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(7045,687,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s',''),(7046,687,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(7047,687,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','<strong>CeboFix R</strong>\r\nPigmentirani fiksator za disanje koji sadrži kvarcno brašno. CeboFix R se nanosi u jednom ili dva sloja, dok se podloga ne pokrije u potpunosti, sa kratkodlakim valjkom. Nakon što se CeboFik R osuši, u slučaju posebno rustikalnih ili nepravilnih podloga, nanesite kremu za gletovanje na bazi kreča CeboFondo.'),(7048,687,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),