krštene i nepravilne poteze. Pre potpunog sušenja, pređite preko površine kako biste blago olakšali reljefne delove. Ako je proizvod previše suv, gletericu navlažite vodom.'),(7068,687,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(7069,687,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_image_f',''),(7070,687,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(7071,687,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_image_s',''),(7072,687,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(7073,687,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_text','<strong>Efekat Sbrecciato:</strong>\r\n\r\nNanesite proizvod gletericom od nerđajućeg čelika, ujednačene debljine 1,5-2 mm. Dok je proizvod još mokar, obradite površinu posebnim CeboSign alatom. Da biste postigli prirodniji efekat, radite na nepravilan način, izbegavajući ponavljanje dizajna. Pre nego što se proizvod potpuno osuši, zagladite površinu gleterom, lagano stežući reljefno delove. Ako je proizvod previše suv, gletericu navlažite vodom.'),(7074,687,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(7075,687,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_2_add_instruction_image_f',''),(7076,687,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_2_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(7077,687,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_2_add_instruction_image_s',''),(7078,687,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_2_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(7079,687,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_2_add_instruction_text','<strong>Efekat talasa Onda:</strong>\r\n\r\nNanesite proizvod gletericom od nerđajućeg čelika, u homogenoj debljini od 1,5-2 mm, vertikalno ili horizontalno u zavisnosti od željenog efekta: zatim pređite preko površine oblikovanom stranom Onda gleterice, prateći smer obrade. Pre potpunog sušenja, pređite preko površine kako biste blago olskunuli ljefne delove. Ako je proizvod previše suv, gletericu navlažite vodom.'),(7080,687,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_2_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(7081,687,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_3_add_instruction_image_f',''),(7082,687,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_3_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(7083,687,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_3_add_instruction_image_s',''),(7084,687,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_3_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(7085,687,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_3_add_instruction_text','<strong>CeboArt Luk:x</strong>\r\n\r\nFina završna obrada za unutrašnjost, na bazi gašenog kreča i prirodnih voskova. CeboArt Luk xbogaćuje površine ukrašene CeboArt modelom, povećavajući dubinu dizajna i dajući mu izuzetan sjaj.'),(7086,687,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_3_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(7087,687,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details','4'),(7088,687,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details','field_61753d07a8579'),(7089,687,'instructions_stages_3_instruction_label_title','Primena CeboArt Luk xa na CeboArt modelu'),(7090,687,'_instructions_stages_3_instruction_label_title','field_61753cf8a8578'),(7091,687,'instructions_stages_3_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f',''),(7092,687,'_instructions_stages_3_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(7093,687,'instructions_stages_3_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s',''),(7094,687,'_instructions_stages_3_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(7095,687,'instructions_stages_3_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','<strong>Primena CeboArt Luk xa na CeboArt modelu</strong>\r\nNa CeboArt modelu, savršeno suvom i bez prašine, nanesite prvi sloj obojenog CeboArt Luk xa sa gleterom od nerđajućeg čelika, vodeći računa da sledite dizajn prethodno kreiran lopaticom. Kada se proizvod osuši na površini (oko 3-4 sata) nanesite drugi sloj. Preporučuje se, na obe ruke, nanošenje tankog sloja proizvoda. Zatim, kada se zid počne sušiti, pređite po površini čistom lopaticom od nerđajućeg čelika da biste dovršili poliranje.'),(7096,687,'_instructions_stages_3_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(7097,687,'instructions_stages_3_instructions_details','1'),(7098,687,'_instructions_stages_3_instructions_details','field_61753d07a8579'),(7099,687,'instructions_stages_4_instruction_label_title','EcoVaCera'),(7100,687,'_instructions_stages_4_instruction_label_title','field_61753cf8a8578'),(7101,687,'instructions_stages_4_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f',''),(7102,687,'_instructions_stages_4_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(7103,687,'instructions_stages_4_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s',''),(7104,687,'_instructions_stages_4_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(7105,687,'instructions_stages_4_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','<strong>EcoVaCera</strong>\r\nPrirodni vosak na vodenoj bazi za unutrašnjost na bazi bijelog pčelinjeg voska i marsejskog sapuna, koji daje vodoodbojnost i povećava prirodni sjaj površina. Pažljivo promešajte proizvod pre nanošenja: ako je gust, razblažite ga sa 5% vrele vode. Nanesite EcoCera tek nakon potpunog sušenja CeboArt Luk -a. Nanesite proizvod sintetičkom spužvom izbegavajući prevelika opterećenja proizvoda; u roku od 30-40 minuta lagano pri ruci vunenom krpom.'),(7106,687,'_instructions_stages_4_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(7107,687,'instructions_stages_4_instructions_details','1'),(7108,687,'_instructions_stages_4_instructions_details','field_61753d07a8579'),(7109,687,'instructions_stages','5'),(7110,687,'_instructions