 i izuzetna estetska vrednost čine proizvode CeboArt linije idealnim kako za savremenu zelenu gradnju, tako i za istorijsko-arhitektonsku restauraciju.'),(7162,692,'_page_main_content_description','field_6175355dc93bd'),(7163,692,'order_product_description',''),(7164,692,'_order_product_description','field_61753591c93be'),(7165,692,'instructions_section_title','Uputstvo za upotrebu'),(7166,692,'_instructions_section_title','field_61753bffa8575'),(7167,692,'instructions_section_description','Priprema podloga: \r\n\r\npogodne su sve gipsane, krečne i cementne podloge. Proverite da li supodloge savršeno čiste, suve i ujednačene po izgledu i upijanju.\r\n<img src=\"http://localhost/zidnedekoracije-new/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Simbolo-NaturalmenteA-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"259\" height=\"118\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-696\" />'),(7168,692,'_instructions_section_description','field_61753c63a8576'),(7169,692,'instructions_stages_0_instruction_label_title','CeboFix R'),(7170,692,'_instructions_stages_0_instruction_label_title','field_61753cf8a8578'),(7171,692,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f',''),(7172,692,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(7173,692,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s',''),(7174,692,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(7175,692,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','<strong>CeboFix R</strong>\r\npigmentni fiksator za paropropusnost koji sadrži kvarcno brašno. CeboFix R se nanosi u jednom ili dva sloja, dok se podloga ne pokrije u potpunosti, sa kratkodlakim valjkom.\r\n'),(7176,692,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(7177,692,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details','1'),(7178,692,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details','field_61753d07a8579'),(7179,692,'instructions_stages_1_instruction_label_title','CeboArt Pintura'),(7180,692,'_instructions_stages_1_instruction_label_title','field_61753cf8a8578'),(7181,692,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f',''),(7182,692,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(7183,692,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s',''),(7184,692,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(7185,692,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','<strong>CeboArt Pintura</strong>\r\nDekorativna boja na bazi prirodnog krečnjačkog gita, antibakterijska, paropropusna, za enterijere i eksterijere. Omogućava postizanje neprozirnih završnih obrada sa delikatnim izgledom tipičnim za tradicionalne krečne boje.\r\n<strong>Nanošenje:</strong> na odgovarajuće pripremljenu podlogu naneti četkom dva sloja CeboArt Pinture, obojen i razblažen 15-20% vodom.\r\n\r\n'),(7186,692,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(7187,692,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details','1'),(7188,692,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details','field_61753d07a8579'),(7189,692,'instructions_stages_2_instruction_label_title','CeboArt Nature'),(7190,692,'_instructions_stages_2_instruction_label_title','field_61753cf8a8578'),(7191,692,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f',''),(7192,692,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(7193,692,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s',''),(7194,692,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(7195,692,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','<strong>CeboArt Nature</strong>\r\nDekorativna boja protiv kondenzacije, za unutrašnjost, na bazi prirodnog krečnjačkog gita, antibakterijska i paropropusna. Poboljšava difuziju vodene pare i ujednačava temperaturne razlike između zidova. Izgled završne obrade karakteriše prijatan mat peskaren efekat.'),(7196,692,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(7197,692,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_image_f',''),(7198,692,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(7199,692,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_image_s',''),(7200,692,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(7201,692,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_text','<strong>Aplikacija:</strong>\r\nBrušeni efekat: Naneti CeboArt Natura, obojen i razblažen 20-25% vodom, u dva sloja sa srednjom četkom (7 × 3 ili 10 × 3), radeći ukrštenim potezima četkice kako bi se dobio niz glatkih i peskovitih.\r\n'),(7202,692,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(7203,692,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_2_add_instruction_image_f',''),(7204,692,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_2_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(7205,692,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_2_add_instruction_image_s',''),(7206,692,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_2_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(7207,692,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_2_add_instruction_text','<strong>Aplikacija:</strong>\r\nPrugasti efekat: nanesite CeboArt Natura, obojen i razblažen 20-25% vodom, u dva sloja srednjom četkom (7 × 3 ili 10 × 3), nastavljajući vertikalnim potezima četke različite dužine: zatim pređite sa praznom četkom za regulisanje poteza i uklanjanje viška proizvoda.'),(7208,692,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_2_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(7209,692,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details','3'),(7210,692,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details','field_61753d07a8579'),(7211,692,'instructions_stages_3_instruction_label_title','CeboSil'),(7212,692,'_instructions_stages_3_instruction_label_title','field_61753cf8a8578'),(7213,692,'instructions_stages_3_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f',''),(7214,692,'_instructions_stages_3_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(7215,692,'instructions_stages_3_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s',''),(7216,692,'_instructions_stages_3_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(7217,692,'instructions_stages_3_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','<strong>CeboSil</strong>\r\nPro i vodoodbojna akrilna siloksanska zaštitna završna obrada, mat izgleda i baršunasta na dodir, za unutrašnjost i spoljašnjost. Ako se nanese na CeboArt Pintura, naglašava nježni chiaroscuro. CeboSil, razrijeđen 1: 1 s vodom, nanosi se u jednom sloju četkom, nastavljajući odozdo prema gore kako bi se izbjeglo kapanje.'),(7218,692,'_instructions_stages_3_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(7219,692,'instructions_stages_3_instructions_details','1'),(7220,692,'_instructions_stages_3_instructions_details','field_61753d07a8579'),(7221,692,'instructions_stages_4_instruction_label_title','CeboFlow'),(7222,692,'_instructions_stages_4_instruction_label_title','field_61753cf8a8578'),(7223,692,'instructions_stages_4_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f',''),(7224,692,'_instructions_stages_4_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(7225,692,'instructions_stages_4_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s',''),(7226,692,'_instructions_stages_4_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(7227,692,'instructions_stages_4_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','<strong>CeboFlow</strong>\r\nProzirna zaštitna sredstva na vodenoj osnovi, koja sadrži posebne fluorisane polimere; formira nevidljivu i vodoodbojnu barijeru, ne menjajući estetski izgled i karakteristike paropropusnosti završnih obrada. Posebno je pogodan za zaštitu od zagađenja vode i atmosfere u spoljnim građevinama. CeboFlow je spreman za upotrebu i može se nanositi četkom, u jednom sloju, dok se površina potpuno ne zasiti. Nastavite sa nanošenjem odozdo prema gore, kako biste izbegli kapanje.'),(7228,692,'_instructions_stages_4_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(7229,692,'instructions_stages_4_instructions_details','1'),(7230,692,'_instructions_stages_4_instructions_details','field_61753d07a8579'),(7231,692,'instructions_stages','5'),(7232,692,'_instructions_stages','field_61753c82a8577'),(7233,692,'slider_or_text','1'),(7234,692,'_slider_or_text','field_6187fa34f0e09'),(7235,692,'half_section_f',''),(7236,692,'_half_section_f','field_61771b4aae9d1'),(7237,692,'half_section_s',''),(7238,692,'_half_section_s','field_61771b6cae9d2'),(7239,692,'background_image',''),(7240,692,'_background_image','field_617722e02e7b3'),(7241,692,'main_content',''),(7242,692,'_main_content','field_617724162e7b9'),(7243,692,'full_width_section',''),(7244,692,'_full_width_section','field_6177246f65aab'),(7245,692,'_yoast_wpseo_primary_kategorija-proizvoda','6'),(7246,692,'_yoast_wpseo_content_score','60'),(7247,692,'_yoast_wpseo_estimated-reading-time-minutes',''),(7248,697,'_edit_last','1'),(7249,697,'_edit_lock','1636320300:1'),(7250,698,'_wp_attached_file','2021/11/Ceboart-Model-E-Cebowax.HEIC-scaled.jpg'),(7251,698,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:6:{s:5:\"width\";i:1920;s:6:\"height\";i:2560;s:4:\"file\";s:47:\"2021/11/Ceboart-Model-E-Cebowax.HEIC-scaled.jpg\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:6:{s:6:\"medium\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:40:\"Ceboart-Model-E-Cebowax.HEIC-225x300.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:225;s:6:\"height\";i:300;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:5:\"large\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:41:\"Ceboart-Model-E-Cebowax.HEIC-768x1024.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:768;s:6:\"height