,697,'instructions_stages_0_instruction_label_title','CeboArt model aplikacija'),(7296,697,'_instructions_stages_0_instruction_label_title','field_61753cf8a8578'),(7297,697,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f',''),(7298,697,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(7299,697,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s',''),(7300,697,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(7301,697,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','<strong>Spatolato efekat:</strong>\r\nNanesite CeboArt model u jednom sloju ujednačene debljine, sa lopaticom od nerđajućeg čelika, a zatim ukrštenim i nepravilnim pokretima stvorite željeni umetnički efekat. Pre potpunog sušenja, ponovo dovršite površinu kako biste izgladili crtež. U slučaju prebrzog sušenja, navlažite površni raspršivačem sa vodom.'),(7302,697,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(7303,697,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_image_f',''),(7304,697,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(7305,697,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_image_s',''),(7306,697,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(7307,697,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_text','<strong>Onda efekat:</strong>\r\nNanesite CeboArt model horizontalno ili vertikalno u sloju ujednačene debljine, koristeći zarezanu stranu gleterice „Shark“ i sa ravnom stranom alata meko zagladite crtež. Dok je proizvod još mokar, obradite površinu PVC lopaticom „Onda 4“, prateći odabrani smjer vodoravno ili okomito. Pre potpunog sušenja, ponovo obradite površinu kako biste lagano izgladili žlebove. U slučaju prebrzog sušenja, navlažite površinu mlazom vode.'),(7308,697,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_1_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(7309,697,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_2_add_instruction_image_f',''),(7310,697,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_2_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(7311,697,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_2_add_instruction_image_s',''),(7312,697,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_2_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(7313,697,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_2_add_instruction_text','<strong>Sbrecciato efekat:</strong>\r\nNanesite CeboArt model dijagonalno u jednom sloju ujednačene debljine, koristeći zarezanu stranu gleterice „Shark“; ponovo dorađujte površinu ravnom stranom dok se ne dobije neprekidna serija glatkih dijagonalnih pruga, različitih veličina. Kada je proizvod još mokar, utapkajte ili izgrebite površinu pomoću alata „CeboSign“ prateći smer crtanja. Pre potpunog sušenja, nežno zagladite žlebove gleterom od nerđajućeg čelika. U slučaju prebrzog sušenja, navlažite površinu mlazom vode.'),(7314,697,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_2_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(7315,697,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_3_add_instruction_image_f',''),(7316,697,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_3_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(7317,697,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_3_add_instruction_image_s',''),(7318,697,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_3_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(7319,697,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_3_add_instruction_text','<strong>Crakuele efekat:</strong>\r\nNanesite CeboFix R valjkom prema izabranoj boji koja će biti boja pukotina. Nakon potpunog sušenja CeboFix R -a, nanesite jedan sloj CeboBreaka ukrštenim potezima četkice sve dok se zasićenje ne završi i površina postane prozirna. Nakon najmanje 4 sata, a maksimalno 24 sata, nanesite CeboArt model sa lopaticom od nerđajućeg čelika u sloju ujednačene debljine: ostvarite željeni umetnički efekat nepravilnim ukrštenim potezima lopatice i sačekajte dok se pukotine ne pojave. Pre potpunog sušenja, nežno zagladite crtež.'),(7320,697,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details_3_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(7321,697,'instructions_stages_0_instructions_details','4'),(7322,697,'_instructions_stages_0_instructions_details','field_61753d07a8579'),(7323,697,'instructions_stages_1_instruction_label_title','CeboBreak'),(7324,697,'_instructions_stages_1_instruction_label_title','field_61753cf8a8578'),(7325,697,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f',''),(7326,697,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(7327,697,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s',''),(7328,697,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(7329,697,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','<strong>CeboBreak</strong>\r\nSrednji prozirni osnovni premaz, koji se koristi za postizanje efekta \"napuknuća\".'),(7330,697,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(7331,697,'instructions_stages_1_instructions_details','1'),(7332,697,'_instructions_stages_1_instructions_details','field_61753d07a8579'),(7333,697,'instructions_stages_2_instruction_label_title','CeboVax'),(7334,697,'_instructions_stages_2_instruction_label_title','field_61753cf8a8578'),(7335,697,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f',''),(7336,697,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_f','field_61753d21a857a'),(7337,697,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s',''),(7338,697,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_image_s','field_61753f5e46e52'),(7339,697,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','<strong>CeboVax</strong>\r\nUnutrašnja završna obrada na bazi prirodnog pčelinjeg voska i odabranih veziva; omogućava stvaranje mekih nijansi, ostavljajući površinu prozračnom i hidrofobnom. CeboVax se može razblažiti vodom do najviše 30%; mora se nanositi sintetičkim sunđerom u jednom ili dva sloja u boji, odozdo prema gore na potpuno suvu površinu.\r\n\r\n<strong>Napomena:</strong> preporučuje se mešanje proizvoda tokom upotrebe.'),(7340,697,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details_0_add_instruction_text','field_61753eed86cc9'),(7341,697,'instructions_stages_2_instructions_details','1'),(7342,697,'_instructions_stages_2_instructions_details','field_61753d07a8579'),(7343,697,'instructions_stages','3'),(7344,697,'_instructions_stages','field_61753c82a8577'),(7345,697,'slider_or_text','1'),(7346,697,'_slider_or_text','field_6187fa34f0e09'),(7347,697,'half_section_f','<h2>Katalog boja</h2>\r\nPrikazane boje su napravljene pomoću digitalnih aplikacija, stoga ih treba smatrati indikativnim i neobavezujućim. Za tačan izbor boja, pogledajte ton karte boja sa pravim proizvodom, koji su dostupni kod ovlašćenih Cebos prodavaca boja.'),(7348,697,'_half_section_f','field_61771b4aae9d1'),(7349,697,'half_section_s','<img src=\"http://localhost/zidnedekoracije-new/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/cartella-CeboArt-Model_web-1024x488-1.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"488\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-703\" />'),(7350,697,'_half_section_s','field_61771b6cae9d2'),(7351,697,'background_image',''),(7352,697,'_background_image','field_617722e02e7b3'),(7353,697,'main_content',''),(7354,697,'_main_content','field_617724162e7b9'),(7355,697,'full_width_section',''),(7356,697,'_full_width_section','field_6177246f65aab'),(7357,697,'_yoast_wpseo_primary_kategorija-proizvoda','6'),(7358,697,'_yoast_wpseo_content_score','60'),(7359,697,'_yoast_wpseo_estimated-reading-time-minutes',''),(7360,704,'_edit_last','1'),(7361,704,'_edit_loc