t_description','field_61753591c93be'),(7964,740,'instructions_section_title','Uputstvo za upotrebu'),(7965,740,'_instructions_section_title','field_61753bffa8575'),(7966,740,'instructions_section_description','<strong>CeboArt model:</strong>\r\nDekorativni premaz velike debljine za unutrašnjost, omogućava izvođenje različitih vrsta izrade; klasična i ujednačena ili inovativna materinska rešenja bez rigoroznih struktura i ograničenja.\r\n\r\n<strong>Priprema površine:</strong>\r\nPovršine od gipsa, kreča i cementa su pogodne, ali moraju biti čiste, suve i ujednačene u pogledu i upijanja.\r\n<strong>CeboFix R:</strong> pigmentirani i paropropusni prajmer, sadrži kvarcni prah. Može se nanositi valjkom sa kratkom dlakom u jednom ili dva sloja do potpunog prekrivanja površine.'),(7967,740,'_instructions_section_description','field_61753c63a8576'),(7968,740,'instructions_stages','4'),(7969,740,'_instructions_stages','field_61753c82a8577'),(7970,740,'slider_or_text','1'),(7971,740,'_slider_or_text','field_6187fa34f0e09'),(7972,740,'half_section_f',''),(7973,740,'_half_section_f','field_61771b4aae9d1'),(7974,740,'half_section_s',''),(7975,740,'_half_section_s','field_61771b6cae9d2'),(7976,740,'background_image',''),(7977,740,'_background_image','field_617722e02e7b3'),(7978,740,'main_content',''),(7979,740,'_main_content','field_617724162e7b9'),(7980,740,'full_width_section',''),(7981,740,'_full_width_section','field_6177246f65aab'),(7982,740,'_yoast_wpseo_primary_kategorija-proizvoda','6'),(7983,740,'_yoast_wpseo_content_score','60'),(7984,740,'_yoast_wpseo_estimated-reading-time-minutes',''),(7985,753,'_wp_attached_file','2021/11/Neoclassici_tabella-finale-2-2-1024x366-1.jpg'),(7986,753,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:1024;s:6:\"height\";i:366;s:4:\"file\";s:53:\"2021/11/Neoclassici_tabella-finale-2-2-1024x366-1.jpg\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:3:{s:6:\"medium\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:53:\"Neoclassici_tabella-finale-2-2-1024x366-1-300x107.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:300;s:6:\